{"tid":2209500,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"數學題","createTime":"2020-09-19T16:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T18:40:21.000Z","uid":306109,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae39cc9b20baf64811848e7f584cb3644b29019","tid":2209500,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:47:32.000Z","msg":"A machine produces items of which 10% are defective.  At the end of each hour, a sample of n items is inspected. If it contains no defectives, themachine is allowed to run for another hour, otherwise the machine is stopped.<br />\n<br />\nb.Find  the  minimum  value  of n if  the  probability  that  the  machine  will  be  stopped  at the end of the first hour is at least 0.3?<br />\n<br />\n呀Sir standard answer <br />\n 1-P(nD)≧0.3 <br />\n=1-0.9^n≧0.3<br />\n=0.7≧0.9^n<br />\nlog0.7≧n log0.9<br />\nlog0.7/log0.9≦n<br />\nn=3.385 <br />\n~4<br />\n<br />\n同我屌你老未直接log(0.9,0.7)=3.385 ~4 得到一樣答案有乜春野分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e68146b03f7e875db83fa15d117676ad56253b7","tid":2209500,"uid":277374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"漏咗咁多點答"},{"pid":"037d12b12873d77443c52199d0cc8cf32ceb4012","tid":2209500,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e68146b03f7e875db83fa15d117676ad56253b7","tid":2209500,"uid":277374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"漏咗咁多點答"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:53:28.000Z","msg":"差D咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba3cbbff08f2c7357c40d3b90bf9ac8c0cbe6d5","tid":2209500,"uid":277374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ae39cc9b20baf64811848e7f584cb3644b29019","tid":2209500,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:47:32.000Z","msg":"A machine produces items of which 10% are defective.  At the end of each hour, a sample of n items is inspected. If it contains no defectives, themachine is allowed to run for another hour, otherwise the machine is stopped.<br />\n<br />\nb.Find  the  minimum  value  of n if  the  probability  that  the  machine  will  be  stopped  at the end of the first hour is at least 0.3?<br />\n<br />\n呀Sir standard answer <br />\n 1-P(nD)≧0.3 <br />\n=1-0.9^n≧0.3<br />\n=0.7≧0.9^n<br />\nlog0.7≧n log0.9<br />\nlog0.7/log0.9≦n<br />\nn=3.385 <br />\n~4<br />\n<br />\n同我屌你老未直接log(0.9,0.7)=3.385 ~4 得到一樣答案有乜春野分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:54:46.000Z","msg":"睇錯，無漏<br />\n<br />\n佢係逐步逐步嚟做啫"},{"pid":"f9575922e500c1a039561639c78868a27b863058","tid":2209500,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"高中以上嘅數學一向都係Method -&gt; Steps -&gt; Answer<br />\n<br />\nlog(0.9,0.7)=3.385 ~4 可以係你睇到問題有嘅數字之下鳩撞出嚟<br />\n<br />\n你得個Answer係Show唔到你識<br />\n<br />\n你覺得自己冇問題嘅話請你返去讀小學"},{"pid":"51926ac76a7782d2c503c4a734fbbb2aab4818bf","tid":2209500,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9575922e500c1a039561639c78868a27b863058","tid":2209500,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"高中以上嘅數學一向都係Method -&gt; Steps -&gt; Answer<br />\n<br />\nlog(0.9,0.7)=3.385 ~4 可以係你睇到問題有嘅數字之下鳩撞出嚟<br />\n<br />\n你得個Answer係Show唔到你識<br />\n<br />\n你覺得自己冇問題嘅話請你返去讀小學"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"1-P(nD)≧0.3<br />\n=1-0.9^n≧0.3<br />\n=0.7≧0.9^n<br />\n=log(0.9,0.7)<br />\nn=3.385<br />\nn~4<br />\n<br />\n咁又點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac150fc372695d5cd8a9625517fbebe8d7b2fed2","tid":2209500,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":