Arr; n log 0.9 &ge; log 0.7<br />\n&rArr; log 0.9^n &ge; log 0.7<br />\n&rArr; 0.9^n &le; 0.7<br />\n&rArr; 0.9^n &le; 1 - 0.3<br />\n&rArr; 1 - 0.9^n &le; 0.3<br />\n&rArr; 1 - P(nD) &le; 0.3<br />\n咁咪同你啊sir一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甚至要寫更多steps<br />\nBtw唔好再用=啦，改用&rArr;就唔會poor presentation<br />\n<br />\nToo long didn&rsquo;t read: 你同啊sir只差在steps，答案冇分別，夠膽就直接出答案，冇滿分蝕底嘅係你自己，完。"},{"pid":"5184ef8d9152408b3824ebf6c35d63b6e5a77de6","tid":2209500,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dd411c8ae129b753ee577664d39f68ca88bcabb","tid":2209500,"uid":75954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"021f54de0d107f6c51dcd6812ba9c215dafae02c","tid":2209500,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6800084f36c6808e020ec5492311dabe475edcd0","tid":2209500,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"哥仔, 好撚基本喎<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係寫埋啲=落去, 你阿sir應該會問你邊度鄉下?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"咁我個計法同呀SIR有無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"至少你都要話俾人知你點得到n &ge; log(0.9,0.7)，0.9係邊度黎，0.7又係邊度黎？log又係邊度黎？我當你真係好撚醒，一眼可以睇穿個答案，但係個制度下你冇step直接出答案就唔會滿分，就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n至少你要寫番啲steps，由題目俾過啲數字10% (0.1)同0.3開始<br />\n如果 part (a) 係搵過P(nD)就可以skip再0.1，因為已經用過一次，但最好話by part (a)<br />\n<br />\n如果你反推番啲steps (令0.7同log還原去題目條件: 冇log同0.3):<br />\n<br />\nn &ge; log(0.9,0.7)<br />\n&rArr; n &ge; (log 0.7) / (log 0.9)<br />\n&rArr; n log 0.9 &ge; log 0.7<br />\n&rArr; log 0.9^n &ge; log 0.7<br />\n&rArr; 0.9^n &le; 0.7<br />\n&rArr; 0.9^n &le; 1 - 0.3<br />\n&rArr; 1 - 0.9^n &le; 0.3<br />\n&rArr; 1 - P(nD) &le; 0.3<br />\n咁咪同你啊sir一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甚至要寫更多steps<br />\nBtw唔好再用=啦，改用&rArr;就唔會poor presentation<br />\n<br />\nToo long didn&rsquo;t read: 你同啊sir只差在